Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.90,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}總是惹怒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:36.82,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}那樣纖細的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:40.72,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}也將與你牽手同行
