Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.92,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}害怕再次放手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:06.52,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}但是我所期待的一切
